---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Thank You! - Hustle Survey">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-zinc-900 flex items-center justify-center">
    <section class="py-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
          <!-- Success Icon -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-24 h-24 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-full border-2 border-zinc-200">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-zinc-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Headline -->
          <h1 class="text-hero font-extrabold text-zinc-50 mb-6">
            thank you! you're on the list
          </h1>

          <p class="text-xl text-zinc-300 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
            your feedback will directly shape HUSTLE
          </p>

          <!-- Personal Letter -->
          <div class="card-slate text-left mb-12 space-y-4 text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>Hi there,</p>

            <p>Thank you for taking the time to complete our survey. I know how busy life gets when you're juggling work, family, and those never-ending sports schedules - so I genuinely appreciate you spending 10 minutes with us.</p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mt-6 mb-4">Let me tell you why I'm building this:</h3>

            <p>I spent 20+ years in the restaurant business, then ran a trucking company for about 5 years before making what seemed like a crazy pivot - diving into AI and technology. People thought I'd lost it. But here's the thing: I've always been drawn to solving real problems for real people.</p>

            <p>Recently, I got accepted into the Google Cloud Startup Program (still feels surreal to say that). But more importantly, I live, eat, and breathe soccer now. And suddenly, all those years of building systems, managing operations, and leveraging technology clicked into place with a new purpose.</p>

            <p><strong class="text-zinc-100">We spend ridiculous amounts of money, time, and energy on our kids' sports.</strong> Tournament fees, travel expenses, private training, equipment - it adds up fast. But here's what drives me crazy: when it comes time for college recruitment, most of us are scrambling through our phones trying to remember stats from games 2 years ago, or hunting down coaches who've long since moved on.</p>

            <p>Our kids' efforts deserve better than that. Every goal, every assist, every improvement should be documented, tracked, and ready to submit when it matters most.</p>

            <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100">That's why I'm building HUSTLE™.</p>

            <p>Not as some fancy tech company looking to make millions (though I wouldn't complain 😄). But as a parent-first solution, built by someone who's been in the trenches - whether that's running a kitchen during a Friday night rush, managing a fleet of trucks, or now, trying to remember which tournament had that incredible save my kid made.</p>

            <p>Your survey responses are going to directly shape this app. I'm reading every single one, and I'll be reaching out to beta testers. If you indicated interest in testing, you'll hear from me personally.</p>

            <p class="italic text-zinc-400 text-sm">Fair warning: while I'm over here talking about building apps and systems, my wife Mandy is the one who actually keeps our family (and this whole operation) running. She's the real MVP - I just get to play with code and pretend I'm busy. 😊</p>
          </div>

          <!-- What Happens Next -->
          <div class="card-slate text-left mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-4">what happens next:</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-300">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-zinc-200 mr-3">→</span>
                <span>if you're selected for beta testing, we'll email you with next steps</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-zinc-200 mr-3">→</span>
                <span>beta testers get <strong class="text-zinc-100">1 year free access</strong> as a thank-you for helping us build something amazing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-zinc-200 mr-3">→</span>
                <span>we'll keep you updated on HUSTLE's progress and launch date</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Share Section -->
          <div class="mb-12">
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">know other sports parents who'd want to help?</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-6">share this survey with your team, club, or parent groups</p>

            <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
              <a
                href="sms:?body=Help build HUSTLE, the ultimate youth sports tracking app! Take this 10-min survey and get 1 year free access: https://intentsolutions.io/survey"
                class="px-6 py-3 bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-zinc-200 hover:border-zinc-400 transition-smooth"
              >
                📱 text
              </a>
              <a
                href="mailto:?subject=Help Build HUSTLE - Youth Sports Tracking App&body=I just completed this survey for HUSTLE, a new youth sports tracking app. They're looking for feedback from competitive sports parents.%0A%0ATake the 10-minute survey and get 1 year free access when they launch:%0Ahttps://intentsolutions.io/survey"
                class="px-6 py-3 bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-zinc-200 hover:border-zinc-400 transition-smooth"
              >
                ✉️ email
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- About Intent Solutions -->
          <div class="pt-12 border-t border-zinc-800">
            <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-4">brought to you by</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-zinc-50 text-xl mb-2">intent solutions io</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">creating industries that don't exist</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-6">gulf shores, alabama</p>

            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-6">
              issues with the survey? <a href="mailto:jeremy@intentsolutions.io" class="text-zinc-300 hover:text-zinc-100 underline transition-smooth">let me know</a>
            </p>

            <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 text-sm mb-8 flex-wrap">
              <a
                href="mailto:jeremy@intentsolutions.io"
                class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-200 transition-smooth"
              >
                email
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://github.com/jeremylongshore"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-200 transition-smooth"
              >
                github
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://jeremylongshore.com"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-200 transition-smooth"
              >
                portfolio
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://startaitools.com"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-200 transition-smooth"
              >
                blog
              </a>
            </div>

            <a
              href="/"
              class="inline-block btn-primary px-8 py-3"
            >
              return to intentsolutions.io
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
